headline: ITRI Teams With Tesla & Xcel to Deploy Virtual Power Plant in Colorado
summary: Itron teams up with Tesla and Xcel Energy to deploy a virtual power plant in Colorado to enhance the management of DERs, maximizing their value and benefits.
